# speckit.plan
## Phase V — Advanced Cloud Deployment & Event-Driven Todo Chatbot

**Version**: 1.0
**Generated**: 2026-03-02
**Generated for**: Phase V complete implementation
**Dependencies**: speckit.constitution v1.0.0, speckit.specify Phase V

---

## Constitution Check — GATE

All sections below MUST comply with constitution v1.0.0. Gates evaluated before design:

| Gate | Rule | Status |
|------|------|--------|
| C-01 | All Kafka communication via Dapr Pub/Sub only (no direct kafka-python) | ✅ PASS |
| C-02 | No polling for reminders or recurring tasks — Dapr Jobs API only | ✅ PASS |
| C-03 | No hardcoded credentials in source or Helm values | ✅ PASS |
| C-04 | All secrets via Dapr secretstores.kubernetes | ✅ PASS |
| C-05 | Every pod has Dapr sidecar injected | ✅ PASS |
| C-06 | Services communicate only via Dapr (Pub/Sub or Service Invocation) | ✅ PASS |
| C-07 | No new databases added (only Neon PostgreSQL) | ✅ PASS |
| C-08 | FastAPI + Python 3.11, SQLModel, Next.js 14 App Router mandated | ✅ PASS |
| C-09 | Minikube (local) → Oracle OKE preferred (cloud) deployment path | ✅ PASS |
| C-10 | GitHub Actions for CI/CD | ✅ PASS |

