### 1.2 Microservice Responsibilities

| Service | Pod Name | Responsibility | Dapr Sidecar |
|---------|----------|----------------|-------------|
| **Chat API** | `todo-backend` | Single entry point — REST + MCP; CRUD; event publisher; Job scheduler | ✅ |
| **Frontend** | `todo-frontend` | Next.js 14 Chat UI; WebSocket client for real-time updates | ✅ |
| **Recurring Task Service** | `recurring-service` | Subscribes `task-events`; spawns next task on TaskCompleted with recurrence | ✅ |
| **Notification Service** | `notification-service` | Subscribes `reminders`; delivers exact-time reminder to user | ✅ |
| **Audit Service** | `audit-service` | Subscribes all 3 topics; writes immutable append-only audit log | ✅ |
| **WebSocket Service** | `websocket-service` | Subscribes `task-updates`; broadcasts to all connected WS clients | ✅ |

### 1.3 Dapr Component Connections

```
Todo Backend ──[pubsub.kafka]──► task-events ──► Recurring Service
                                              └──► Audit Service
             ──[pubsub.kafka]──► reminders   ──► Notification Service
                                              └──► Audit Service
             ──[pubsub.kafka]──► task-updates ──► WebSocket Service
             ──[dapr-jobs]───► Scheduler (fires at due_date → publishes to reminders)
             ──[state.postgresql]─► Neon DB (conversation state, task cache)
             ──[secretstores.kubernetes]─► K8s Secrets (DATABASE_URL, KAFKA, OPENAI)

Recurring Svc ──[service-invocation]─► Todo Backend POST /internal/tasks
```

