## 9. Acceptance Criteria for Plan Completion

The plan is considered complete when all of the following checkpoints are verifiable:

| ID | Checkpoint | Verification |
|----|-----------|-------------|
| AC-P01 | All 6 service pods running with Dapr sidecar (2/2 Ready) on Minikube | `kubectl get pods -n todo-app` |
| AC-P02 | All 3 Dapr components show Ready status | `kubectl get components -n todo-app` |
| AC-P03 | Strimzi Kafka cluster Ready on Minikube | `kubectl get kafka -n kafka` |
| AC-P04 | POST /tasks publishes to task-events topic (verified via Dapr logs) | Dapr sidecar logs show `[dapr.pubsub]` publish |
| AC-P05 | TaskCompleted event triggers next task creation (recurring) | Recurring-service logs show next task created |
| AC-P06 | ReminderFired event at exact due_date (±5s) | Notification-service logs show delivery at expected time |
| AC-P07 | All audit events appear in audit log within 5s | GET /audit returns entry for every published event |
| AC-P08 | WebSocket client receives update within 2s of PATCH | Browser DevTools WS frame shows update |
| AC-P09 | All 6 service images successfully pushed to registry with correct SHA tag | `docker pull ghcr.io/.../todo-backend:<sha>` |
| AC-P10 | GitHub Actions: lint + test + build + deploy all green | GitHub Actions tab shows all jobs ✅ |
| AC-P11 | Production deploy gate requires manual approval | GitHub Environment `production` shows pending reviewer |
| AC-P12 | No secret appears in any Helm values or source file | `grep -r "DATABASE_URL" charts/ src/` returns no results |
| AC-P13 | OKE cloud deployment: all pods Running, Ingress accessible | Browser loads frontend via OKE external IP |

